examples.en: A castle perched on the summit.

The house is perched atop a hill amid a stretch of dense woodland.

examples.en: The house was perched on an overhanging cliff in a most dangerous position.

examples.en: Bobby had perched himself on a tall wooden stool.

examples.en: He wore spectacles perched on the very end of his nose.

examples.en: The tree had a stout branch, and I found the boy perched there on his hunkers.
